description: This 6ft USB 2.0 cable features two USB ''A'' male connectors, delivering a dependable way to connect your PC to a USB hub, or connect USB 2.0 peripherals to a USB hub. Fully rated to USB 2.0 performance specifications, this high quality USB cable is backed by StarTech.com''s Lifetime Warranty.
title: StarTech.com Beige A to A USB 2.0 Cable - M/M (USBFAA_6)
